brynrhodes pushed 14 commits to branch br-substantive-changes.

  • J#30204, J#21005: Removed CQFQuestionnaire profile and added reference to Structured Data Capture (bc30255)
  • J#29430: Renamed PlanDefinition.action.relatedAction.actionId to targetId (a70b358)
  • J#27923: Changed ActivityDefinition.location to CodeableConcept; added location to PlanDefinition and RequestGroup action (c26c7ca)
  • J#27752: Added the ability to reference relatedData in input/output data for actions (2101fd4)
  • J#25471: Removed dateTime and Period choices from timing elements in ActivityDefinition and PlanDefinition (1b8c872)
  • J#25056: Added a useCarePlan parameter to $apply and changed output type to Resource to support both CarePlan and RequestGroup as output (95d6822)
  • J#20728: Reduced PlanDefinition.action.code cardinality to 0..1 (ee89e78)
  • J#19786: Additional documentation for the CDS Hooks indicator code system (347e06a)
  • Fixes from full build (df24341)
  • J#22680: Changed cqf-initialValue and cqf-calculatedValue to be of type Expression (a24a2ff)
  • Full build fixes (8262719)
  • J#20825: Added actor and participant.function to PlanDefinition. (c68fb1d)
  • J#24618: Allowed definitional participants in RequestGroup (f83e1f0)
  • J#24618: Allowed definitional participants in RequestGroup (141414c)

  • J#31480 (dd762a0)

  • FHIR-25512 - Require names on variable extension (f03a153)
  • Update structuredefinition-profile-vsd-alignedvalueset.xml (4823d5c)
